oracle linux installguide - https://docs.oracle.com/en/operating-systems/oracle-linux/9/install/index.html#Oracle-Linux-9
test media
particionamento manual
excluir discos
particionamento automatico
lvm
server gui
definir senhas
instalar

configurar swap:
sudo dnf install zram-generator
sudo vim /etc/sysctl.d/99-sysctl.conf
vm.swappiness=1
vm.vfs_cache_pressure=50
vm.dirty_background_bytes=16777216 
vm.dirty_bytes=50331648 

configurar dnf:
Para isso, abra um terminal e digite:
sudo nano /etc/dnf/dnf.conf
max_parallel_downloads=10
fastestmirror=true
deltarpm=true

atualizar:
sudo dnf upgrade --refresh 
sudo dnf update

habilitar repositórios do gnome-software e adicionar repositórios:

sudo dnf install --nogpgcheck https://dl.fedoraproject.org/pub/epel/epel-release-latest-$(rpm -E %rhel).noarch.rpm

sudo dnf install --nogpgcheck https://mirrors.rpmfusion.org/free/el/rpmfusion-free-release-$(rpm -E %rhel).noarch.rpm https://mirrors.rpmfusion.org/nonfree/el/rpmfusion-nonfree-release-$(rpm -E %rhel).noarch.rpm

flatpak:
sudo dnf install flatpak
flatpak remote-add --if-not-exists flathub https://flathub.org/repo/flathub.flatpakrepo
sudo reboot

snap:
sudo dnf install snapd
sudo systemctl enable --now snapd.socket
sudo ln -s /var/lib/snapd/snap /snap
sudo reboot

instalar pacotes:
sudo dnf install  dnf-automatic ntfs-3g lm_sensors speedtest-cli vim neovim mc geany git curl testdisk ddrescue qphotorec smartmontools gsmartcontrol hwinfo lshw-gui htop yum-utils tmux tmate timeshift gnome-tweaks dia gimp inkscape blender fish redshift ark filezilla arj cabextract p7zip lzip unrar unzip zip

mudar o shell:
chsh -s /usr/bin/fish

habilitar o cockpit:
sudo systemctl enable --now cockpit.socket
sudo firewall-cmd --add-service=cockpit
sudo firewall-cmd --add-service=cockpit --permanent
sudo firewall-cmd --reload

instalar navegador:
https://dl.google.com/linux/direct/google-chrome-stable_current_x86_64.rpm

teamviewer:
https://www.teamviewer.com/pt-br/download/linux/

configurar usuarios, serviços online, navegador e configurações de energia.



